display="inline"><![CDATA[P_1]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[P_2]]></fr:tex> agree on all of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\sigma (\mathscr {P})]]></fr:tex>.
